{"tid":1282172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會被示威者衝擊破壞，涉及金額七百億元?????","createTime":"2019-07-03T13:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:18:30.000Z","uid":150921,"like":132,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b14807422152a7bee4b258b838efbbc10315010e","tid":1282172,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:31:17.000Z","msg":"係我聽錯定點? 岩岩聽到電視話涉及七百億元，<br />\n而唔係話財會撥款七百億元延期??<br />\n真心希望係我聽錯，而唔係有人斷章取義。<br />\n岩岩即刻聽到老母講: 嘩，要用咁多錢.....<br />\n真係會誤會咗係維修費或者係延期開支<br />\n財會撥款延期包括<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員加薪</span></strong><br />\n呢點係想引起公務員不滿<br />\n政府不斷強調各維修同涉及金額既意圖好明顯<br />\n就係想贏返民意!!!<br />\n你知D廢老隻耳唔多靈，就算電視無講錯，佢都地可能會聽錯。<br />\n佢地唔會上網，主要靠電視同落公園圍爐傳資訊，<br />\n我地之前既長輩圖有一定成效<br />\n唔好比佢停，呢段時間可以做文宣!!!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各單位唔好放軟手腳!!，<br />\n輿論戰依家先開始!!!</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972177373d57a8a630915f4b1fec2671fc963d14","tid":1282172,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d73cde5de4e1d80fe9fb18cd09d51cc0107d3982","tid":1282172,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"［文宣戰對準台灣］蔡英文要做多d助攻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282101</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0f09d0bc5ae749d9471ed6eef591bb372afb1843","tid":1282172,"uid":68598,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"其實公務員WFC <br />\n儲錢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922f89eb896dbf190f95264f5c03a1e5cdf63d2e","tid":1282172,"uid":108337,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"cit